    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just exhausting. every morning i wake up and i have to put the mask back on. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it's like the real me died a long time ago and i'm just a ghost haunting my own body. what's the point of keeping up the act if there's nothing left inside?",
